msgstr ""

#: ../../appendix/upgrade-notes/2.x-to-3.0.rst:468
msgid "The subtable ``sites_entity`` for ``ElggSite`` no longer exists. All attributes have been moved to metadata. The subtable ``groups_entity`` for ``ElggGroup`` no longer exists. All attributes have been moved to metadata. The subtable ``objects_entity`` for ``ElggObject`` no longer exists. All attributes have been moved to metadata. The subtable ``users_entity`` for ``ElggUser`` no longer exists. All attributes have been moved to metadata."
